summary: 1963  was a common year starting on Tuesday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: Kenneth "Kenny" Wallace  is an American professional stock car racing driver. He retired from NASCAR after a 2015 Xfinity Series race at Iowa, where he competed in the No. 20 Toyota Camry for Joe Gibbs Racing in a one race deal. In a career spanning twenty-five years in NASCAR, Wallace had nine wins, all occurring in the Xfinity Series. Now retired from NASCAR competition, he continues to race on local dirt tracks across the country as a hobby.
title: Kenny Wallace
